So, what did you take from me?

538
00:36:40,280 --> 00:36:44,240
我在想你带在身上的照片
I was thinking the photograph that you carry.

539
00:36:44,320 --> 00:36:46,120
那个飞行员女孩
That girl. The pilot.

540
00:36:47,030 --> 00:36:49,030
你带在身边的那张
The one you carry on you.

541
00:36:51,160 --> 00:36:55,370
但你被偷走的已经够多的了
But you've had enough stolen from you already.

542
00:36:56,960 --> 00:37:00,130
不知何故...我想我会设法把这个还给她的
I'll try and get these back to her somehow.

543
00:37:01,420 --> 00:37:03,760
后面还有一个口袋
The other pocket, at the back.

544
00:37:10,640 --> 00:37:12,890
守卫从她那里拿走
The guards took it from her.

545
