I still have a case pending.

547
00:37:29,740 --> 00:37:31,330
如果你想要帮忙
If you want to help,

548
00:37:33,000 --> 00:37:34,830
如果你敢帮这个忙
if you dare to help,

549
00:37:35,830 --> 00:37:37,630
把这个还给我的当事人
get this to my client.

550
00:37:37,710 --> 00:37:38,710
案子?
A case?

551
00:37:38,790 --> 00:37:40,460
我有职业操守
I have a calling,

552
00:37:40,630 --> 00:37:43,510
在我耳边不断地提醒我
so the ringing in my ears tells me.

553
00:37:51,600 --> 00:37:53,850
好吧  你最好解释一下这个
Okay, you better explain this.

554
00:37:54,640 --> 00:37:56,270
我甚至不知道这是什么
Don't even know what it is.

555
00:37:56,350 --> 00:37:58,770
我知道  你从哪儿拿来的?
Well, I do. Where did you get it?

556
00:37:58,860 --> 00:38:02,020
那个把你当小学生一样教训的人
The one that scolded you like a schoolboy,

557
00:38:02,860 --> 00:38:06,610
妈的  用用你的脑子  他的名字? 严肃先生
frakking with your head. What's his name? Mr. Serious.

558
00:38:08,320 --> 00:38:09,490
凯利
Kelly.

559
00:38:11,450 --> 00:38:12,790
凯...凯利?
Kelly?

560
00:38:12,870 --> 00:38:13,990
是的
Yeah.

561
00:38:26,220 --> 00:38:30,220
你在那架猛禽机上 我是绝对不会上雅典娜升空的
I never would have let Athena go airborne with you in the Raptor.

562
00:38:31,100 --> 00:38:33,430
你知道  我会阻止的
I would have stopped it. You know that.

563
00:38:33,520 --> 00:38:34,810
是  我知道
Yeah, I know that.

564
00:38:35,270 --> 00:38:37,020
你最好把我关起来
You better lock me up.

565
00:38:38,190 --> 00:38:40,980
我不想要什么审判 我不会停止的
And I don't want any trial. I won't stop.

566
00:38:42,480 --> 00:38:44,230
我会继续尝试
I will keep trying.

567
00:38:44,780 --> 00:38:46,740
我会坚持不懈  我会的
I'll keep at it, I will.

568
00:38:47,280 --> 00:38:49,070
我做了自己的工作  长官
I did my job, sir,

569
00:38:50,320 --> 00:38:53,120
我已经干了两年
and I have done my job for two years now.

570
00:38:54,830 --> 00:38:57,410
每天我送人们去战场
Every day, I sent people out to fight,

571
00:38:58,250 --> 00:39:00,290
然后帮他们收尸
I cleared them all to die.

572
00:39:03,170 --> 00:39:04,750
那么多人
So many people.

573
00:39:06,050 --> 00:39:08,590
我不想再这样子下去了
I just got tired of living with that.

574
00:39:09,220 --> 00:39:11,840
你问问那个人  如果要选 
You ask that man, if he had to choose

575
00:39:13,930 --> 00:39:16,850
是为人类死  还是为赛昂死?
between giving his life up for a Cylon or a human,

576
00:39:16,930 --> 00:39:19,020
你猜他会怎么说
what do you think he'd say?

577
00:39:20,230 --> 00:39:22,100
我必须做点什么
I had to do something.

578
00:39:23,570 --> 00:39:27,440
副长  恢复阿达玛少校…
XO, reinstate Major Adama

579
00:39:27,530 --> 00:39:29,740
的空军飞行队长身份
as Commander of the Air Group.

580
00:39:30,450 --> 00:39:32,320
立即生效
Effective immediately.

581
00:39:35,790 --> 00:39:37,870
很高兴你回来了
It's good to have you back.

582
00:39:38,410 --> 00:39:39,410
谢谢
Thank you.

583
00:39:39,500 --> 00:39:42,330
很抱歉 我错了  
I'm sorry. I guess I was wrong.

584
00:39:44,170 --> 00:39:45,750
我把事情搞得更糟糕了   不  
I made it worse. No.

585
00:39:45,840 --> 00:39:47,340
不 你知道你应该在你的战机里
No, you should be in your bird.

586
00:39:47,420 --> 00:39:49,800
我想我该和拉姆金在一起
I think I should be with Lampkin.

587
00:39:50,300 --> 00:39:52,760
既然我们知道了是凯利干的
Well, now that we know that it was Kelly,

588
00:39:53,470 --> 00:39:55,510
我们就可以稍微放松一下安全措施了
we can ease up a little bit on security.

589
00:39:55,600 --> 00:39:58,560
就拉姆金的身体状况来看 我想他需要人帮他准备审判 
In his condition, I think Lampkin needs help preparing the trial,

590
00:39:58,640 --> 00:39:59,730
陈述案情
presenting his case.

591
00:39:59,810 --> 00:40:03,520
总统还有些其他候选人 她在考虑
The President has a few possibilities. She's looking.

592
00:40:03,730 --> 00:40:05,310
爸  为什么不是我?
Dad, why not me?

593
00:40:06,360 --> 00:40:09,400
我熟悉案子  读过文件
I'm close to the case, I've read the documents.

594
00:40:09,820 --> 00:40:11,650
我了解拉姆金的策略
I understand Lampkin's strategy.

595
00:40:11,740 --> 00:40:13,820
事情都在我们控制之中
We have things under control.

596
00:40:14,660 --> 00:40:16,830
拉姆金会得到帮助的
Lampkin will have help.

597
00:40:17,330 --> 00:40:18,620
我想做这个
I wanna do this.

598
00:40:18,700 --> 00:40:20,160
你是空军飞行队长
You're a CAG.

599
00:40:20,250 --> 00:40:23,620
你不是律师 差的远了
You're not a lawyer. Far from it.

600
00:40:23,710 --> 00:40:25,750
难道你就是法官了?
What? And you're a judge?

601
00:40:25,840 --> 00:40:28,710
不是  但就像其他四个被挑选出来的人
No. But like the four other men picked,

602
00:40:28,960 --> 00:40:32,050
我有能力采纳证据  
I'm capable of listening to the evidence

603
00:40:32,130 --> 00:40:34,640
作出合理的判断
and making an ethical decision.

604
00:40:34,720 --> 00:40:37,220
我有能力辅助拉姆金
And I'm capable of helping Lampkin.

605
00:40:37,510 --> 00:40:38,810
别说了
Forget it.

606
00:40:38,890 --> 00:40:40,520
我要你当好空军飞行队长
I need you as CAG.

607
00:40:41,560 --> 00:40:43,850
那你为什么给我这些书?
Why did you give me those books? Huh?

608
00:40:43,940 --> 00:40:46,190
我是说  你给了我你父亲的法律书
I mean, you gave me your father's law books.

609
00:40:46,270 --> 00:40:47,560
我犯了个错误
I made a mistake.

610
00:40:47,650 --> 00:40:49,150
为什么  为什么是个错误?
Why? Why is it a mistake?

611
00:40:49,230 --> 00:40:50,940
你怕我变成他那样?
Are you afraid that I'll be like him?

612
00:40:51,030 --> 00:40:52,110
你是飞行员
You're a pilot.

613
00:40:52,200 --> 00:40:54,660
因为扎克和卡拉都死了
And with Zak gone and Kara gone, you need someone

614
00:40:54,740 --> 00:40:55,910
你需要有人把旗帜扛起来  是吗?
to carry the flag. Is that it?

615
00:40:55,990 --> 00:40:57,700
你是飞行员并且你是我儿子
You're a pilot and you're my son.

616
00:40:57,780 --> 00:41:02,660
我不想看到你坐在法庭的另一边
I will not look across that court and see you sitting on the other side.

617
00:41:03,750 --> 00:41:06,630
看到我?  还是看到其他人?
See me? Or see someone else?

618
00:41:06,710 --> 00:41:08,340
回去报到吧
Report for duty.

619
00:41:09,210 --> 00:41:10,880
这是命令吗?
Is that an order?

620
00:41:11,880 --> 00:41:14,090
你跑题太远了
You're in way over your head.

621
00:41:14,470 --> 00:41:15,510
回去报到
Report for duty.

622
00:41:15,590 --> 00:41:17,180
这是命令吗?!
Is that an order?

623
00:41:25,060 --> 00:41:27,230
我不会再对你下命令了
I'm through giving you orders.

624
00:41:32,990 --> 00:41:36,910
把阿波罗开除出甲板 通知西洛他还是空军飞行队长
Remove Apollo from the board. Inform Helo he's to remain at CAG.

625
00:41:37,660 --> 00:41:40,580
我儿子还有更重要的事要照料
My son has more important things to tend to.

626
00:42:10,940 --> 00:42:12,730
嘿  腿怎么样了?
Hey, how's the leg?

627
00:42:13,740 --> 00:42:15,820
你是说我中的大奖吗?
You mean my lucky break?

628
00:42:17,610 --> 00:42:20,320
给了我个不来这儿的理由
Gave me a reason not to come up here.

629
00:42:23,200 --> 00:42:24,950
迟早
Sooner or later,

630
00:42:25,620 --> 00:42:27,620
你会用完借口的
you run out of excuses.

631
00:42:30,210 --> 00:42:32,040
很难就这样让她走了...
It's hard to let her go.

632
00:42:35,840 --> 00:42:37,010
李
Lee...

633
00:42:39,140 --> 00:42:40,970
回头见
I'll see you around.

